Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Gotcha!\N- Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer. It's the season of love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is burning a young lady's bare body\Nthe sun's mischief?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the quivering of asphalt\Na heat haze mirage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A boy and girl\Nbare their hearts to each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and are invited to take the next step\Nin a male-female relationship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The curtain comes up\Non a summer vacation like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half a month has passed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}During that time,\Nnothing in particular has happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}AUGUST
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I totally screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}SHOPPING\NFIREWORKS FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was that a sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you sigh like that,\Nhappiness will flee in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}AI HAYASAKA\NWANTS TO GET SOAKED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President Shirogane\Nsays he's at home right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so if you loiter around outside,\Nyou may see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't talk silly, Hayasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As if I would engage in stalker-like—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He says he's at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayasaka, since when have you been\Nin contact with the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He was grumbling about it on Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Twitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's that? No, I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Twitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think Miss Fujiwara does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}DICTIONARY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Twitter... Twitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}RESERVED
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}FEMALE EMPLOYEES'\NBATHROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She gets to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SPLASH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FSSS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayasaka! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Internet is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It must be the major incident\Nof the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I tried to start doing that thing,\Nyou know, Twitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}USER NAME\NEMAIL ADDRESS\NI AGREE TO THE TERMS\NOF SERVICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but the letters are garbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The letters are not garbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Password.\NCan I use my bank password?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Hopeless at I.T.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}HOPELESS AT I.T.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it comes to technology,\NKaguya prefers to be analog.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can do mental arithmetic,\Nbut cant use a calculator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she looks into something, she'll use\Na map or encyclopedia instead of googling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}ENCYCLOPEDIA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She does use the Internet once in a while\Nto check the weather or news headlines,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but never leaves the confines\Nof the search engine site's top page.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's about as tech-savvy as the old man\Nwho runs the candy shop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}YAMADA STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Now you have an account,\NLady Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NCHIKA FUJIWARA\NYU ISHIGAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I printed out the accounts\Nof the other student council members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For example,\Nthis is the secretary's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}I WENT TO DUBAI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}I WENT TO CALIFORNIA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She clearly spends a great deal of time\Ntweeting and no time at all studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}I WENT TO BALI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}I WENT TO HAWAII
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All she does is travel abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And this anime icon is the treasur—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The best thing to do is play around\Nwith it until you're used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going back to my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This job is exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The only way I can take it\Nis by washing my fatigue away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lady Kaguya doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}She should appreciate me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayasaka! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lady Kaguya,\Nwould you stop barging in on—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've been banned from Twitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you even know\Nabout being banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}THIS ACCOUNT'S TWEETS\NARE PROTECTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}L-Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't see it! Why?\NDid I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President Shirogane\Nhas a protected account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's because some trolls will flame you\Nno matter what you post.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}This goes to show that the president\Nis on his toes about privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}My main account is protected, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'd better be very careful, too,\NLady Kaguya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,think of your account as your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With normal accounts,\Nthe front door is wide open,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so visitors can come and go\Nas they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But cautious people\Nkeep their front door locked,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and only visitors\Nwho are given a key can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, where do you get a key?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FOLLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}LIKES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you click this "Follow" button,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,a request for approval\Nwill be sent to President Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If he agrees,\Nyou'll then be able to see his tweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I imagine he'd okay any request, as long as\Ntheir profile shows they go to Shuchiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But... But I... But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, it would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}President! Please open up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know more about you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}REQUESTING APPROVAL\NFOR A FOLLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I want to know what you think about\Nand what you usually do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}BAM BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You want to know about me that badly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're that interested\Nin my 140-character monologues?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's cute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}APPROVED
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is this a new kind of stupidity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really think\Nof the most useless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you mad at me, Hayasaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mad? More like I'm wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,how long you're going to make me\Nstand around half-naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you won't do it, Lady Kaguya, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll do it when I'm good and ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FOLLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}LIKES
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what the president\Ntweets about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he doing? What does he like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How is he spending his summer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's it! I'll protect my account, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Then, if the president follows me—\N- Wake up and smell the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've never succeeded\Nwith that pattern before. Not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end,\Nshe wasn't able to send the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lady Kaguya is stubborn to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They both are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If either were open about their feelings,\Nthey could both be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I envy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish I loved someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayasaka! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}None.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KAGUYA AND SHIROGANE DIDN'T MEET UP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CLICK CLICK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}HER TYPING IS VERY FAST
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}CHIKA FUJIWARA\NREALLY WANTS TO EAT IT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I loved Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish we could've stayed there\Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The ta'amiya and kushari were delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're just thinking about food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe you wanted to stay longer, Sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I couldn't wait to get back to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Saburo Odajima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an insignificant middle manager.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}HAKATA TENRYU
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My hobby is frequenting ramen shops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}TENRYU RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came to a neighborhood shop today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most popular item on the menu\Nis pork bone broth ramen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that's not for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get the inconspicuous one\Nall the way at the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Soy sauce pork bone. Thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about the noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is this shop's optimum combination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way I ordered\Nshows I'm in the know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It smells wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, well, a cute customer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she wandered in\Nthinking this was a cake shop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What can I get you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,soy sauce pork bone ramen, thin broth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did a girl like this suddenly calculate\Nthis shop's optimum combination?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}OPTIMUM COMBINATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it a coincidence? No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't the kind of shop a young woman\Nwould enter alone this late at night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}RAMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this woman be one of "my people"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MY PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What about the noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,super-firm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}FSSS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super-firm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like a sheep,\Nshe chose the fad level of firmness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's just an average girl after all.\NI worried for nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I overestimated her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, then. I'll teach this girl\Nthe real way to eat ramen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, you note the scent\Nof the soup itself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The idea is to appreciate\Neach scent in turn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}starting from the fragrant\Nred pickled ginger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Of course, the owner is fully aware of that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm delighted at his consideration,\Nplacing the ginger farthest away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next, the taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Letting the air mix in while you taste it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I use my brain completely,\Nsharpening my senses of smell and taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, the noodles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bite off a small amount,\Nas if making sure of the flavor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and enjoy it as it slides down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, the chaser.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to enjoy the delicate flavors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I drink water to wash away the soy and salt\Non my tongue, resetting my palate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This makes all the difference.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is one set.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repeating the set over and over\Nis what we call the "water cycle."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, what about you, young lady?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mini-ramen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Little bits. Little bits. Little bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She really is just an ordinary girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}GOBBLE...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Looks like she's enjoying it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Well, I can't really look down on her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mini-ramen,\Nwhere you eat it all in each bite,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}is the ultimate form\Nof the "one is all" philosophy after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Little bits. Little bits. Little bits.\NLittle bits! Little bits. Little bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But by taking little bites like that,\Nthe noodles will stretch out and swell up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Swell up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super-firm! Super-firm! Super-firm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Is that why she said, "Super-firm"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did this girl calculate\Nthat the noodles would stretch out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Slurp, slurp, slurp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Moreover, using that small utensil\Nis perfect for mini-ramen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this was all calculated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The metro's four ramen kings...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jinbocho's Mashimashi Mama,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Hermit of Sugamo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}even J. Suzuki of Koenji...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE METRO AREA'S\NBIG FOUR RAMEN KINGS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}JINBOCHO'S\NMASHIMASHI MAMA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}J. SUZUKI OF KOENJI\NHERMIT OF SUGAMO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}So, she possesses the sense\Nof situational assessment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}equivalent to the monsters\Nof the ramen world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}SAN OF SHIBUYA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Not yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's right. She's not there yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's kind of sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the wall that can't be overcome,\Nand it's owing to being a woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Garlic!\N- Garlic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately, avoiding that scent\Npegs her as a wannabe ramen connoisseur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a fake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like she finished\Neating the ingredients.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What is she gonna do now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}There's no more to spoon out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What's she gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she gonna go for it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's gonna go for it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}CRUNCH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She went for it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She overcame the wall of womanhood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to give her props!\NShe's earned my respect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's definitely "my people"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ramen connoisseur!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Even the soup?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too much salt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're drinking garlic, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}...there was a time in my life, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for the meal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I become such an old man?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GULP GULP
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it! Run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That youth is the radiance I lost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm young and starving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep running!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}POLISHED IT OFF
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Boom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}COOL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Result of today's ramen match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}RESULT OF TODAY'S RAMEN MATCH:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}FUJIWARA WINS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}WHERE IS YOUR SWITCH?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My ramen switch is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}MIYUKI SHIROGANE\NWANTS TO SEE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since summer vacation began,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}three weeks have passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing of note\Nhas happened during that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Days of studying, working, eating,\Ntaking a bath, sleeping, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This has become\Na boring summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The festival at the end of vacation\Nis the only plan{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}he and Kaguya made to see each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Other than that,\Nthey haven't exchanged a single text,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}let alone go out together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The high hurdle of asking the other person\Nto go out and do something fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}is still insurmountable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It wasn't supposed to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder what Shinomiya's doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't supposed to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why has it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason, Lady Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}is that, all your plans are based on the premise\Nthat the president is going to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}SUMMER VACATION PLANS\NFOR KAGUYA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've been too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hayasaka, why are you looking\Nat your lady's notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so brazenly and without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you just ask him\Nto do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It'd look like I wanted to do something\Nfor fun with the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's exactly right.\NI mean, you're not even refuting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}TO: KAGUYA SHINOMIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shi-no-mi-ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What-are-you-doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}DELETE THIS MAIL?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}SAVE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DELETE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Am I some blushing girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,WHAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Write, delete, write, delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is this, your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It is his first love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}AUGUST
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's it! I'm done! I'm through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}SUBJECT: OCTOPUS\NLOOK! A LIVE OCTOPUS!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}FROM: SHIROGANE\NI WAS TRYING TO TELL YOU SOMETHING\NAS YOU HUNG UP THE PHONE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}LOOKS LIKE TONIGHT WILL GET\NPRETTY COLD, SO BE WARM\NAND GO TO SLEEP\NGOOD NIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No matter how much you read that,\Nit won't make new messages appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did that message make you so happy\Nthat you've saved it all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The president's first text to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You were thrilled when he made\Nthe first move there, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can't forget it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't think that at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so stop trying to analyze my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grocery shopping for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In your school uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I may stop at school on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The school isn't on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What I'm doing now doesn't make any sense.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I thought, "What if," and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice and cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}STUDENT COUNCIL ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I wish summer vacation weren't so long.\N- I wish summer vacation weren't so long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH: NONE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BECAUSE THEY DIDN'T MEET UP
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have any summer memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's not a problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I've never gone on a family vacation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But that's okay...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}because everyone treats me\Nlike I'm special.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never gone to see\Na fireworks display.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's all right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}because even the little lights\NI see from out my window are pretty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}FROM: MISS FUJIWARA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}LET'S MEET UP IN FRONT OF\NTHE MOAI STATUE TOMORROW!\NI CAN'T WAIT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never gone shopping\Nwith a group of friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, I felt a mix\Nof anxiety and anticipation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But it would be okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The people I was going with\Nwere good people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}They were all very nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm used to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't do what I want in this life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}FROM: KAGUYA\NSUBJECT: TOMORROW - I'M SORRY.\NI CAN'T GO SHOPPING TOMORROW.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"My father suddenly summoned me\Nto the main house in Kyoto, so I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. All of you\Nshould go on and have fun, okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we put it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The whole point\Nis for all of us to go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll call Kei and let her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm blessed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got friends and a distinguished family\Nthat anyone would envy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm blessed with a resourcefulness\Nthat anyone would be jealous of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone would conclude that the amount\Nof my happiness and sorrow are about the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, blessed as I am,\Nit's only logical that I should suck it up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He summoned you\Nall the way here for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Drop dead, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My father has never said\N"good night" to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't remember him\Never saying "See you later,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Good job" or "I love you" to me either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it doesn't hurt my feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because it's always been this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}By this point, nothing he does\Nmakes me feel one way or the other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In deference to my family's status,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}people around here\Nbehave a certain way toward me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}with great caution...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}as if there's no problem...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}like I'm a creepy\Ntraditional Japanese doll.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}After all, I'm going\Nto a fireworks festival tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}I CAN'T HEAR\NTHE FIREWORKS, PART 1
